{
  "_comment": "A `kubectl get ... -o json` slice. PerspectiveGraph auto-discovers the exposure path internet \u2192 Ingress \u2192 Service \u2192 Pod \u2192 ServiceAccount \u2192 cluster-admin, plus Pod\u2192Image (so a scanner CVE on the image lands on a reachable path). Includes an internet-exposed privileged pod (metrics-agent) that ESCAPES_TO cluster-admin (container escape, ATT&CK T1611).",
